  API

  Signup: http://localhost:3000/signup?email=matetushar@gmail.com&password=matetushar&firstname=Tushar&lastname=Mate

  Signin: http://localhost:3000/signin?email=admin@gmail.com&password=1234

  Add Blog:
  http://localhost:3000/blog/addblog?title=my first blog&body=my first blog description&published=yes

  Show Blog:
  http://localhost:3000/blog/show/1

  Add Comment:
  http://localhost:3000/blog/addcomment?body=this is blog comment&id=2